# Rob's Solar / Rob's Finance — root environment reference
#
# Copy the app-specific examples instead of filling this file:
#   backend/.env.example  → backend/.env
#   frontend/.env.example → frontend/.env.local
#
# Typical local URLs:
#   Frontend  http://127.0.0.1:3000
#   Backend   http://127.0.0.1:8000
#   Health    http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
#
# Hosted: set BACKEND_URL for the Vercel → Render proxy (see README).
